with vcr.use_cassette('test_notifications_dismiss.yaml',
    cassette_library_dir='tests/cassettes_pre_2_9_2', record_mode='none'):
    status = None
    try:
        status = api2.status_post('@mastodonpy_test hello!')
        notifications = api.notifications()
        api.notifications_dismiss(notifications[0])
    finally:
        if not status is None:
            api2.status_delete(status)
